{"tid":105911,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[純發洩]你地班仆街諗好左食咩先叫人過黎落單啦","createTime":"2017-02-03T09:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T15:28:13.000Z","uid":12618,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49d2d8a9877ac977e4ed158b038fd40e5ad7fd8c","tid":105911,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:00:05.000Z","msg":"我唔係做樓面 但我鄧佢地慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說今日去食晏  大家都知食晏時間侍應實好忙<br />\n咁啱我就坐正係兩枱閪客中間<br />\n後面果枱坐左兩個廢老<br />\n前面果枱坐左廢中一家<br />\n<br />\n首先講廢老果枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個叫大辣一個叫中辣<br />\n我心諗咁食得辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲野黎到食兩啖 話好辣  叫個侍應黎比杯水沖一沖淡<br />\n比左之後不停係度loop話好辣食唔到<br />\n之後再叫個侍應過黎話食唔到 煮過碗清湯比佢<br />\n你係唔知大辣中辣有幾辣可以試下叫小辣先<br />\n一黎就叫咁辣你唔煩人地覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n煮左出黎食左兩啖又話唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪咁嘥野啦屌  人地唔加你料都偷笑<br />\n<br />\n之後到廢中一枱果枱 真係極品黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落單都未諗要食乜  <br />\n人地黎到先開始同屋企人傾要乜<br />\n叫左一樣之得又話唔好 <br />\n如是者loop左三次  侍應覆一次單都仲話要改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落單落左成五分鐘終於落完<br />\n到啲野食黎到  個侍應放低無十秒佢即刻舉手<br />\n我以為侍應比錯野佢 原來唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係叫人過黎問呢啲係咩黎<br />\n我以為佢唔知一樣姐<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌</span></span>佢樣樣問呢樣咩黎呢樣咩黎<br />\n唔知佢金魚記憶定點  好似完全唔知自己叫左乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要每樣食物都要介紹可以去過第二間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個侍應都好忙 根本無乜時間去應酬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以上都係純發洩 我知我有啲八掛 人地做乜關我乜事  <br />\n但有時真係睇唔過眼啲人咁岸鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6136e4e035a92ac163d2cbf66e6785e806661a9","tid":105911,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05965bb7ce2f8a8c66f5e21f7b9a7ea4002da3c1","tid":105911,"uid":33410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:11:37.000Z","msg":"廢老渣ga"},{"pid":"ed2839f226c68fcabcedbabcd83ce2249a9c7f2a","tid":105911,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a761320a43bbdf724be40b8e3e143978bbc49274","tid":105911,"uid":34757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:23:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0dd048445b17f082b73fff6c5acbf43f26e4cdb","tid":105911,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"喂寫野呀<br />\n(侍應企係到等)<br />\n喂你地食咩呀,慢慢揀啦"},{"pid":"438ec761ffa0f4ca3eb127b4d360b097fc3737ac","tid":105911,"uid":50935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:27:01.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"c8243c7c69ba72b73db1a0393ad83452541843bf","tid":105911,"uid":60508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"香港人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e655c2ad443edc1ede0a22c916432b3c6aff84","tid":105911,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:38:44.000Z","msg":"樓主你應該要一路狂話個廢老&quot;渣ga&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1797a9b98b81ad6988ee1c531607c641a045792","tid":105911,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你應該要一路狂話個廢老&quot;渣ga&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有講<img src=\"/assets/fac